housing.title: California infill builder turns idle lots into housing in land-constrained coastal markets
housing.what: City Ventures redevelops underused land in coastal California, adding new homes in markets with severe land constraints and housing shortages.
housing.why: Supply pipeline sets future inventory and construction activity.
housing.market: Stronger pipeline aids suppliers; oversupply later can weigh on pricing.

housing.title: Connecticut rolls back zoning limits to target housing shortage
housing.what: Connecticut’s zoning reform enables more housing, restricts algorithmic rents, and incentivizes towns to adopt growth plans.
housing.why: Rent moves feed shelter inflation and multifamily fundamentals.
housing.market: Rising rents help MF REITs; falling rents ease inflation but pressure NOI.
